---
layout: layouts/section.njk
title: Safety Notices
summary: Current and archived unmanned aircraft safety notices issued by the EAA.
permalink: /safety-notices/
breadcrumbs:
  - title: Safety Notices
---
<p>Safety notices provide timely instructions and advisories for operators and remote pilots. Check this page regularly before undertaking operations.</p>
<ul class="list-clean">
{% for notice in collections.notices %}
  <li class="card">
    <h3><a href="{{ notice.url }}">{{ notice.data.title }}</a></h3>
    <p><strong>Reference:</strong> {{ notice.data.reference }}<br><strong>Issued:</strong> <time datetime="{{ notice.date | isoDate }}">{{ notice.date | ukDate }}</time></p>
    <p>{{ notice.data.summary }}</p>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
